> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141321688034dc16fd57f06cc137ebdbc311223a","tid":625753,"uid":142854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"幾值得玩<br />\n但去到越後越難有方向<br />\n尤其是涉及source code果d<br />\n未見過真係唔會諗到"},{"pid":"e6e296d8db81ba5299e3fc8aeb47285fde11951a","tid":625753,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"第五關<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.deathball.net/notpron/google/screen5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.deathball.net%2Fnotpron%2Fgoogle%2Fscreen5.jpg&h=24e29324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>eyes like an angel smiles like a devil</blockquote><br />\n唔識咪Google...<br />\n原來係Big Daddy Voodoo Daddy嘅Simple Songs入面嘅歌詞<br />\n睇蒞條友好鍾意呢隊Band<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n㩒遙控粒開關制登入<br />\nusername: simple<br />\npassword: songs"},{"pid":"ecd7ee4e9c3a81a83a55274432d5a6861332560a","tid":625753,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c075e56272911fbe8418115a36aa6d8725465fbd","tid":625753,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:53:13.000Z","msg":"第六關<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/014119_00dabe35e436033eb497152db42d68c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F014119_00dabe35e436033eb497152db42d68c5.png&h=f7457878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果用電話一睇就睇到下面有兩行特別嘅數字<br />\n用電腦就要手動highlight或者睇原始檔<br />\n<blockquote>108 105 108 107<br />\n117 111 114 104</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係ASCII?<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.asciitable.com/index/asciifull.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asciitable.com%2Findex%2Fasciifull.gif&h=caa9a203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nASCII係電腦編碼系統，可以將數字、拉丁字母變成數字傳輸<br />\n將上面兩行轉返做拉丁字母會得到<br />\n<blockquote>lilk<br />\nuorh</blockquote><br />\n㩒左下角個圓圈登入<br />\nusername: lilk<br />\npassword: uorh<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n錯撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果用電腦喺登入會見到提示<br />\n<blockquote>The site says: &quot;anagram&quot;</blockquote><br />\nAnagram即係將字母次序調亂構成嘅新字<br />\nlilk, uorh嘅anagram..<br />\nusername: kill<br />\npassword: hour<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa98213b41ee94cb835f4dbb21c767ab1f6c195a","tid":625753,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"141321688034dc16fd57f06cc137ebdbc311223a","tid":625753,"uid":142854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"幾值得玩<br />\n但去到越後越難有方向<br />\n尤其是涉及source code果d<br />\n未見過真係唔會諗到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"隔離post嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5983787eb89f21394f437c57e946fe8fc5cde753","tid":625753,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:30:47.000Z","msg":"第七關（卡咗一陣關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/021337_c13ac0b6593f62d02e915bed6ab3bd60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F021337_c13ac0b6593f62d02e915bed6ab3bd60.png&h=ac1bce11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係睇source code...<br />\n<blockquote>times have changed in deutschland</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>what candy wrapper is it?</blockquote><br />\n個包裝應該係一隻叫Twix嘅朱古力<br />\n有花生醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://resources.supplychaindigital.com/styles/slider_detail/s3fs/topic/image/TWIX2.jpg?itok=_CyewEnk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2